STATE
v.
Lee Edward HUTCHENS. No. 21P16-1. Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 17, 2016. Craig M. Cooley, Cary, for Hutchens, Lee Edward. Barry H. Bloch, Assistant Attorney General, for State of North Carolina. Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, for State of North Carolina. David Learner, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 28th of January 2016 by State of NC to Dismiss Appeal:

"Motion Dismissed as moot by order of the Court in conference, this the 17th of March 2016."
